{
  "stem": "25639.8",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And these things were so heavy, and the slave laborers had to lift them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- it's totally different now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It-- it seemed like Kinderspiel, or children's play, compared to the process that existed during World War II.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a young girl of 15, I-- I-- [? sometimes-- ?] I really experience many, many things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As you can see, one can only talk about a segment of these experiences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if I remember this much, I-- I must have experienced much more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But thank god for the lapse of time, for its healing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I forget more and more and it is good.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It is good.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's important to remember the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and actually, I'm sort of commenting on the-- on the total area, that I want to be able to tell you many more details, and I'm sure, that after this interview is over with, I will think of lots of other examples.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as of this moment, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Ravensbruck was a camp, to me, when I was the weakest in my entire life, when I was totally emaciated, and I was suffering from-- from malnutrition.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My right leg was completely full of holes, full of deep holes that refused to heal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It started really just before we-- I went to Beendorf, already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there, it was just little pimples.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First a couple, then five, six, and then 10 or 12, and then they would fuse together and would become larger and deeper, and they would become infected, and we had no medical care, whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I always felt that we must go on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We just can't give up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I must let mother know that I am alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She really was my magnetic force.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
